data.description: Check out this three-bedroom home with vaulted ceilings! Located a very short distance from shopping, dining, recreation, and local dog park! Beautiful laminate flooring in main living areas. In your new white kitchen, you have stainless steel range and dishwasher. In the primary bedroom, you have a good size walk-in closet, and the primary bathroom has dual sinks and additional storage. Very good size guest bedrooms. Need storage space? In your new garage ready for you is a workshop area with plenty of storage! But that's not all! There is also a storage room with built-in shelving! Let's not forget about the low-maintenance backyard! And keep your tools protected from the weather in the storage shed. See this home today!
